  "body": "# Patches\nEverything old is new again\n\n<img alt=\"Available for Ornithe\" src=\"https://badger-api-staging.worldwidepixel.ca/compact?gradientStart=ff5b4d&gradientEnd=442d32&lineOne=Available%20for&lineTwo=Ornithe&colourOne=ffffff&colourTwo=85c2ff&iconUrl=https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/96929194\">\n<img alt=\"Requires Ornithe Standard Libraries\" src=\"https://badger-api-staging.worldwidepixel.ca/compact?gradientStart=ff5b4d&gradientEnd=442d32&lineOne=Requires&lineTwo=OSL&colourOne=ffffff&colourTwo=85c2ff&iconUrl=https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/96929194\">\n\n## 📖 About\nA spiritual successor (or perhaps precursor) to Sprint, this mod aims to improve various QoLs of legacy Minecraft.\n\nCurrently includes:\n- Skin and cape fixes\n- Addition of player sprint\n\n## ❓ FAQ\n- Will this mod support more than one Minecraft version at a time?\n  - No. Due to the nature of the development cycle of this mod, it is impossible to provide long term support to specific versions.",
